parse.title: J.R.R. Tolkien - Master of Middle Earth Calendar 1990

wikitext.*:
[[Image:J.R.R. Tolkien - Master of Middle Earth Calendar 1990.jpg|thumb]]

'''J.R.R. Tolkien - Master of Middle Earth''' was published by [[Miles Kimball]] of Oshkosh, WI. The calendar is unique in that it spans the period from August 1990 to August 1991 instead of a standard calendar or academic year.

* Dimensions: 10 x 20 inches (opened for hanging)
* Metal tab with punched hanging hole
* White comb-bound
